            <p>After a vet visit, submit your itemized invoice through the insurer's app or website. Claims are typically processed in 2-14 days (Lemonade does it in seconds). Once approved, you receive reimbursement via direct deposit or check. Some insurers like Trupanion pay the vet directly, eliminating the wait entirely.</p>
